      "name": "Voyage Culinaire Zurich",
      "abstract": "Enjoy a culinary experience consisting of team spirit, fun and sightseeing!",
      "description": "This culinary event is composed of a guided tour through Zurich and gastronomic team activities revolving around the topics of food and drink. Enjoy a 3-course menu in 1-2 different venues and a wine presentation of the wines you have selected for dinner.",
